entries.content:
Found the issue! Codex indicator has smaller icon and text than Claude indicator:

CODEX (ui-indicator-dna.css):
- Icon: 12px x 12px
- Text: 8px

CLAUDE (ui-indicator-claude.css):  
- Icon: 18px x 18px
- Text: 10px

Difference: Claude icon is 50% larger (18px vs 12px), text is 25% larger (10px vs 8px)
